    <abstract>
      <t>The Diameter base protocol leverages either IPsec or SSL for integrity and confidentiality between two Diameter nodes. The base protocol also defines a Diameter proxy server, that forwards requests to other servers when it detects that a given request cannot be satisfied locally.</t>
